In re B.O. No. 2017-0191 Supreme Court of Ohio. Submitted November 21, 2017
Decided January 16, 2018* Paul D. Dolce, for appellant, B.O. O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, Fischer, and DeWine, JJ., concur. French and O'Neill, JJ., dissent. --------

*242{¶ 1} This cause is dismissed as having been improvidently accepted.

Reporter's Note: This cause was decided on January 16, 2018, but was released to the public on January 31, 2018, subsequent to the resignation of Justice William M. O'Neill, who participated in the decision.
